      "span_text": "The fluctuations obtained in are true for any β > 0, in the case of Hermitian matrices, for a large class of (polynomial) potentials, and for a large class of functions f (in its full generality, Johansson's work is applicable to H 17/2 functions, where H α stands for the corresponding Sobolev space)."
